{"chapter_id":"yhzp.volume-five.selected-passages","diplomatic_text":"身弱論","id":"yhzp.seg.volume-five.body-weak-heading","layer":"editorial","locator_ids":["loc.yhzp.v4.17.body-weak-heading"],"normalized_search_text":"身弱論","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"chapter_heading_attestation"}
{"chapter_id":"yhzp.volume-five.selected-passages","diplomatic_text":"偏官如虎怕沖多，運旺身強豈奈何。身弱虎強成禍患，身強制伏貴中和。","id":"yhzp.seg.volume-five.killing-strength-verse","layer":"yuanhai","locator_ids":["loc.yhzp.qin.50.killing-strength"],"normalized_search_text":"偏官如虎怕沖多運旺身強豈奈何身弱虎強成禍患身強制伏貴中和","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"conditional_strength_claim"}
{"chapter_id":"yhzp.volume-five.selected-passages","diplomatic_text":"土臨卯位三合全，不見當生金水纏。火木旺鄉名利顯，再逢坤坎禍連綿。","id":"yhzp.seg.volume-five.follow-killing-earth-verse","layer":"yuanhai","locator_ids":["loc.yhzp.qin.69.follow-killing","loc.yhzp.v4.9.follow-killing"],"normalized_search_text":"土臨卯位三合全不見當生金水纏火木旺鄉名利顯再逢坤坎禍連綿","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"named_pattern_attestation"}
{"chapter_id":"yhzp.volume-five.selected-passages","diplomatic_text":"庚日全逢寅午戌，天干透出始為神。重重火旺聲名顯，命裏休囚忌水鄉。","id":"yhzp.seg.volume-five.follow-killing-metal-verse","layer":"yuanhai","locator_ids":["loc.yhzp.qin.69.follow-killing"],"normalized_search_text":"庚日全逢寅午戌天干透出始為神重重火旺聲名顯命裏休囚忌水鄉","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"named_pattern_attestation"}
{"chapter_id":"yhzp.volume-five.selected-passages","diplomatic_text":"沐浴那堪吉位逢，更兼引從在其中。讀書必定登科甲，莫比諸神例作凶。","id":"yhzp.seg.volume-five.education-verse","layer":"yuanhai","locator_ids":["loc.yhzp.qin.76.education","loc.yhzp.v4.12.education"],"normalized_search_text":"沐浴那堪吉位逢更兼引從在其中讀書必定登科甲莫比諸神例作凶","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_education_claim"}
{"chapter_id":"yhzp.volume-five.selected-passages","diplomatic_text":"夫格局者，自有定論，今略而述之。印綬見財行財運又兼死絕，必入黃泉。如柱有比肩，庶幾有解。","id":"yhzp.seg.volume-five.pattern-life-death-seal","layer":"yuanhai","locator_ids":["loc.yhzp.qin.86.life-death-seal"],"normalized_search_text":"夫格局者自有定論今略而述之印綬見財行財運又兼死絕必入黃泉如柱有比肩庶幾有解","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_fatality_claim"}
{"chapter_id":"yhzp.volume-five.selected-passages","diplomatic_text":"正官見殺及傷官，刑沖破害歲運相併，必死。","id":"yhzp.seg.volume-five.pattern-life-death-officer","layer":"yuanhai","locator_ids":["loc.yhzp.qin.86.life-death-officer"],"normalized_search_text":"正官見殺及傷官刑沖破害歲運相併必死","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_fatality_claim"}
